---
title: Roasted Duck Breasts with Mushroom and Farro Pilaf
description: This Discovery dinner is all about classic flavours! Juicy duck, toasted farro and pan-roasted mushrooms come together to create a hearty meal. A touch of sweet and savoury balsamic glaze brings it all together.
